    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about needing rest though. it's the fact that even when i rest, the same stuff happens again. it's like a pattern that's already written out. no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. it's just... inevitable at this point.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
